Package: linkwizard
Version: 1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: python, python-pip
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://telegram.me/nullxvoid
Description: Powerful profile link finder for Termux
 Searches DuckDuckGo for a term, filters results to domains in domains.txt,
 and common profile paths. Extracts profile links and generates a stylish
 HTML report. Domain list can be managed with 'linkwizard domains ...'.
